title: PENTAKILL AND BARON STEAL!!!

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: Today was a normal sunny afternoon when i decided to play league. then.......... at that moment............. when all 5 enemies were at the baron pit.......... I GOT A PENTA AND STOLE BARON!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! :) :) :)
